Who We Are

Both of us teamed up to create a website to show tourists the beauty of Cebu.

Our Mission is to boost and promote Cebu, A beautiful place in Visayas. We ensure satisfaction, that anyone who enter our website leaves satisfied and happy.

Heart Jayan R. Obsioma

Click to edit text

Heart Jayan R. Obsioma, creator of the website, a grade 9 student from SRCB, dedicated all her time into making something that others can benefit from. She made this to help people know on what to expect when going there and help them be prepared for an amazing, comfortable, and delicious time in Cebu.
